title: Episode 26 - Jane Saville Interview (Brink Vault 2009)
itunes:title: Episode 26 - Jane Saville Interview (Brink Vault 2009)
description: Today we bring you the first in a special of 'vault' interviews, where we bring you classic interviews from our parent show The Brink with Olympians and other people involved in the Olympic Games. Our first is an interview with Athens Bronze medalist race walker Jane Saville from 2009, as she takes us through her amazing career and details THAT moment from Sydney 2000 that still stands as one of the most sad sporting moments ever seen in Australian sporting history.
